{"tid":1507172,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【企出嚟】你哋一小步，香港一大步","createTime":"2019-08-26T04:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T07:30:11.000Z","uid":217234,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"797c2b8a3ebfa7ac4a5e01e51ccb659c3d466ae8","tid":1507172,"uid":217234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"【代朋友出】<br />\n大家好，<br />\n我地打算向聯合國的Human Rights Council循International Covenant on Civil and Political Rights (ICCPR)向香港政府，in particular，香港警隊作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n香港作為ICCPR締約方，並且將ICCPR納入成為Hong Kong Bill of Rights的憲法一部分，有責任保護及履行ICCPR中的人權法。然而，過去三個月，香港政府和警隊明顯地breach左ICCPR中的：<br />\n<br />\n1) Art. 7 &amp; Art. 10: No one shall be subjected to torture/degrading treatment /punishment  &amp; those who deprived liberty shall be treated with humanity; <br />\n<br />\n2) Art. 9: Arbitrary arrest and detention; and <br />\n<br />\n3) Art. 21: Right of peaceful assembly - the legality of 不反對通知書 &amp; arrest during lawful assembly.<br />\n<br />\n我們將以香港市民的身份向聯合國提出上述投訴，complaint drafting和legal research正在進行中。同時間，如果你有受到以上任何其中三點的human rights deprivation，我們誠邀你加入作為香港市民的聯署。<br />\n<br />\n如果你，第一身，或你身邊人有受到直接的暴力對待甚至無理拘捕，而又願意加入我們這次投訴，你的經歷和署名將令我地呢份complaint更加有力。但請放心，你嘅身份絕對可以要求保密，即是你嘅身份不會被香港政府知道，只需要去話俾聯合國我呢份complaint有證據去support，去接受我嘅申請，香港政府只會知道件事嘅facts，所以我好希望你哋可以企出嚟去成就呢份complaint。<br />\n<br />\n為表誠意和顯示出呢次complaint的真確性，圖中的email是我本人作為是次complaint的&rdquo;author&rdquo;的私人email。如有任何疑問，或者你願意加入聯署，請feel free email我，或者DM ig: knowyourrightshk ； tg:angiete / fightforhomgkong<br />\n<br />\n警隊配備武裝，但行為乖戾放肆、無法無天。而本港法例對於控告警隊和警員亦有好多制肘。我們必需要令佢地明白: be you ever so high, the law is above you. <br />\n<br />\n感謝各位，感謝香港人。🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opuvTfN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopuvTfN.jpg&h=3cec9314&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65eed885459c14ab672e4fc2ed96cb6947ab40ce","tid":1507172,"uid":217234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:03:45.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"5264a826adb677c89b79fcfc18daf532f8e4bb66","tid":1507172,"uid":217234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"2e9f7215181fb5a745e7f295ea5f123ac5f2cfaa","tid":1507172,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjbVjJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjbVjJ3.jpg&h=4677b5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=1df655bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DhSUAso.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDhSUAso.jpg&h=aaca1d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=1df655bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"a6c828a16c9932f6aece4fcd67b02320a0192fee","tid":1507172,"uid":217234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:04:05.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"5e07c722b41bf6da5f44ffe4ca1312363dd2e958","tid":1507172,"uid":217234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:04:15.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"3bb94b7605280425154da6bf7c5499a13f39e8b5","tid":1507172,"uid":217234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"eaa3ee98972552cc65ddb408946f23724e40c5c1","tid":1507172,"uid":217234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"21e2bcc24d30b2cbbef5e9d379949f17756207b1","tid":1507172,"uid":217234,"like":0,"